Cell["\<\
The Fock states of a many-Fermion systems are not mere tensor-product states \
of the Fock states of individual Fermions. One has to be careful about the \
Fermi statistics.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1742225965,ExpressionUUID->"890fed20-0d7b-4ced-9b91-26ab10b39617"],

